title: Microsoft CTO: AI Startups Must Experiment Now, Not Wait for Better Models
description: Microsoft CTO Kevin Scott urges AI startups to stop waiting for superior models and immediately experiment with current tools, as barriers to entry are low and rapid prototyping drives innovation.
